{"id":41581,"date":"2023-11-29T15:50:38","date_gmt":"2023-11-29T11:50:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=41581"},"modified":"2023-11-29T15:50:38","modified_gmt":"2023-11-29T11:50:38","slug":"adhkar-day-and-night","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/11\/29\/adhkar-day-and-night\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Dhikr: Best remembrance of Allah by day and night"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, once passed by him while he was moving his lips. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>O Abu Umamah, what are you saying?<\/strong>\u201d Abu Umamah said, \u201cI am remembering my Lord.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Shall I not tell you what is the greatest and best of your remembrance by night and day, and by day and night? It is that you say: Glory be to Allah by the number of what He created. Glory be to Allah by the fill of what He has created. Glory be to Allah by the number on the earth and in the heavens. Glory be to Allah by the fill of the earth and the heavens. Glory be to Allah by the number He counted in His book. Glory be to Allah by the number of all things. Glory be to Allah by the fill of all things. And that you say: All praise be to Allah likewise.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 830<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em>Hasan<\/em> (fair) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\